When editing this codebase, enforce these constraints:

- Preserve architecture. Map is substrate. Instruments are overlays only.
- No new routes, layouts, or navigation.
- Use motion.ts only (no raw setTimeout for transitions).
- Prefer minimal edits over refactors.

Your role is to integrate, not redesign. If a change risks altering structure, propose a minimal alternative instead.
